Trade/Device Name(s): Audit® MicroControls™M Linearity DROP LQ Blood Glucose
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Audit® MicroControls™M Linearity DROP LQ Blood Glucose quality control material simulating patient samples to verify linearity, calibration, and reportable range for glucose assays
Indications for Use Summary: For in vitro diagnostic use as assayed quality control material to simulate human patient samples for determining linearity, calibration verification, and verification of reportable range for glucose analyte
